# iOS / SwiftUI stack

When editing SwiftUI / Xcode / `project.yml`:
- Load and follow **figma-swiftui** for design ↔ Swift work
- Work on an agent-owned `codex/*` branch and deliver only through the protected pull-request workflow; never push directly to `main`
- Never tell Adam to open Xcode, run xcodegen, or wait for TestFlight to verify routine changes
- Prefer `ssh studio` for builds when not already on a Mac worker
